Subject: how do i generate and email a report of changes in an AD security group
Description: i would like to generate a report and email it, of changes made to a group, i.e adding and deleting members
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c:
Expand the job
Expand Configure
Click on Report
Click on Create
What_We_Know__c: The customer is looking to create a personalized report for their client.
Solution_Comment__c: I created the Report for the customer.
